Tyrael: I have to speak with you, Shadow Star. Talon, find the third 
planet of this system and place us on high orbit. Report when you're 
done. Lieutenant, come in my office, please.

The glowing robot walks away and into the room he called his office. 
He waits for Shadow Star.
